Time To Event Dataset

aqs(ADSL, FUN = function(p) {     PARAMCD <- c("BFIALL", "FATIGI",
  "FKSI-FWB", "FKSI-TSE", "FKSIALL")     PARAM <- c("BFI All Questions",
  "Fatigue Interference", "Function/Well-Being (GF1,GF3,GF7)",
  "Treatment Side Effects (GP2,C5,GP5)", "FKSI-19 All Questions")    
  nvisits <- ceiling(runif(1) * 10 + 1)     data.frame(USUBJID = p$USUBJID,
  STUDYID = p$STUDYID, PARAMCD = rep(PARAMCD, each = nvisits), PARAM =
  rep(PARAM, each = nvisits), AVAL = rnorm(length(PARAM) * nvisits), AVISIT
  = paste("WEEK", 1:nvisits), AVISITN = rep(1:nvisits, length(PARAM)),
  ABLFL = rep(rep(c("Y", ""), c(1, nvisits - 1)), length(PARAM)), APBFL =
  rep(rep(c("", "Y"), c(1, nvisits - 1)), length(PARAM)), stringsAsFactors
  = FALSE) %>% mutate(CHG = AVAL - AVAL[1], PCHG = CHG/AVAL[1]) }, ...,
  start_with)
